metadata.description: The AstroNots is a collection of 10,000 unique Astronaut (or AstroNot) NFTs. The collection is centered around a stop-motion animated TV show called, you guessed it The AstroNots. This show brings together comedy, sci-fi, crypto, and NFTs. The overall project roadmap goes on to create more shows and films in crypto that can be collected under one roof. The ultimate objective is to create a library of media, only accessible by NFTs. So strap on your helmet and take the journey with us. Visit www.theastronots.io and www.wonderblockstudios.com to stay up to date on project details.
